    "description": "<p><strong>Faith is about what you do. It's about aspiring to be better and nobler and kinder than you are.</strong></p><p><em>– Jim Butcher, Changes</em></p><p>Channelers of the magic of creation, luminaries are philosophers, muses, and healers of the people.</p><h3>Iconic Luminaries</h3><ul><li><strong>Aerith Gainsborough</strong>, <em>Final Fantasy VII</em></li><li><strong>Goldmoon</strong>, <em>Dragonlance</em></li><li><strong>Nynaeve Sedai</strong>, <em>The Wheel of Time series</em></li><li><strong>Ophilia Clement</strong>, <em>Octopath Traveler</em></li></ul><h3>Playing Luminary</h3><p>Luminary is a high support magic healer. It's recommended that you refrain from direct melee.</p><p><strong>Action:</strong> Cast<br /><strong>Move:</strong> Midline/Backline<br /><strong>Starting Pack:</strong> Devout<br /><strong>Key Stat:</strong> Awareness<br /><strong>Complexity:</strong> ★★★☆☆</p><h3>Training</h3><p><strong>Weapons:</strong> –<br /><strong>Skills:</strong> Mysticism, and 3 from either Arcana, Detect, Influence, Leadership, or Medicine</p><p></p><h3><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Class Features</span></h3><table class=\"NormalTable\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color:rgb(255,255,255);font-size:9pt\">Level</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color:rgb(255,255,255);font-size:9pt\">Features</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"82\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color:rgb(255,255,255);font-size:9pt\">Mana</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\"><p><span class=\"fon